The Inspect Deployment panel displays detailed information on an active deployment of a resource on a tenant and allows to download the log files.&nbsp;

> Tip

To access the Inspect Deployment panel, click ![](data:image/png;base64,) (**More**) and select **Inspect **next to an active deployment in the Release &amp; Deploy panel.

For more information, see: [Doxee Platform Repository - Release &amp; Deploy Panel](/doxee-platform/docs/doxee-platform-repository-release-amp-deploy-panel), section "Actions on active deployments".
